The third round of World Cup group matches start today, with hosts Russia back in action.

Two Group matches are being played simultaneously. Hence, four matches will be played a day in the third round fixtures.

Here are the World Cup fixtures for today:

Mon June 25: Uruguay v Russia (Group A) - Samara, 3pm

Mon June 25: Saudi Arabia v Egypt (Group A) - Volgograd, 3pm

Mon June 25: Spain v Morocco (Group B) - Kaliningrad, 7pm

Mon June 25: Iran v Portugal (Group B) - Saransk, 7pm